<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="thankful-adj">thankful <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'θæŋkfl/    美 /'θæŋkfl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>感激的；欣慰的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We must be <strong>thankful for</strong> small mercies.
对小小的恩惠我们也必须心存感激。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My mother is thankful that I have won the scholarship.
我获得了奖学金，妈妈很欣慰。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>thankfully /'θæŋkfəli/ adv   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li><strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (thankful), I managed to get through the game and the pain was worth it in the end.  （2011 安徽改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. Thankfully  </p></div>